endation-al-mustahab","tag-sunnah","tag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9pa","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":7645,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/best-nalf-salat-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":36156,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Best voluntary prayer offered at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"O people, perform prayer in your houses, for the best prayer of a man is in his house, except for the prescribed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 731 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/01\/salat-nawafil-at-home\/","url_meta":{"origin":36156,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Perform voluntary prayers at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you finishes the prayer in his mosque, let him perform a portion of his prayer in his house. Verily, Allah will bring about good from his prayer in his house.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 778\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salat-after-fajr-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36156,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salah: No voluntary prayers after Fajr and \u2018Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer after the morning prayer until the sun has risen, and there is no prayer after the afternoon prayer until the sun has set.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 552, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 626 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28159,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/witr-beginning-middle-end\/","url_meta":{"origin":36156,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet prays Witr before dawn","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would perform Witr prayer every night, either at the beginning, middle, or end of the night, finishing his Witr prayer before the break of dawn. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 996, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 745 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-after-friday-in-his-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":36156,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Friday: The Prophet prays after Friday in his house","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not pray after Friday prayer until he had departed and thus would pray in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 895, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 882 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4288,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/fajr-rakaat-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":36156,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: The Prophet would sometimes pray lightly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would sometimes perform two cycles of prayer before the dawn prayer so lightly that I would say to myself, \"Did he recite Surat al-Fatihah?\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1165, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 724 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u00a0according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u